168
00:11:51,139 --> 00:11:52,979
Hey, you're bleeding. Right here!

169
00:11:59,489 --> 00:12:01,619
My gosh. You're so tough.

170
00:12:05,590 --> 00:12:07,159
Wait, hold on.

171
00:12:26,550 --> 00:12:28,180
Where is he? That little...

172
