284
00:19:19,090 --> 00:19:20,129
Se Gyeong.

285
00:19:27,629 --> 00:19:28,800
What's wrong, Se Gyeong?

286
00:19:29,199 --> 00:19:30,240
What's going on?

287
00:19:30,639 --> 00:19:31,669
Se Gyeong?

288
00:19:33,340 --> 00:19:34,368
