776
00:51:41,799 --> 00:51:43,569
Do you want to watch this band with me?

777
00:51:43,900 --> 00:51:44,940
From Se Gyeong.

778
00:51:50,110 --> 00:51:51,779
Sir, I can't work today.

779
00:51:52,080 --> 00:51:54,080
